<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head><script type="text/javascript">var __startTime = new Date().getTime();</script>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title></title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/global.css" type="text/css"></link>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jquery.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jend.js"></script>
		<style type="text/css">
			.methods li.explain .expList{
			    width: 1160px;
			}
			.methods li.explain .expList dd{
			    width: 49%;
			}
			.methods li.explain .expList dd pre {
			    margin-left: -495px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header></header>
		<aside class="menu"></aside>
		<article class="menuCon">
			<div class="listmod">
				<h3 class="conTitle"></h3>
				<p>查看源码： <a href="rem.source.js" class="bold uline  tag" target="_blank">/static/js/libs/rem.js</a></p>
				<P>1、页面默认采取750宽度为标准等价于1rem根元素字体；来计算页面大小适应各个移动设备；</P>
				<P>2、特殊页面不以750宽度设计；可以在根元素（html）设置<span class="atn">data-pagewidth</span><span class="pun">=</span><span class="atv">"xxx"</span>来修改默认宽值；</P>
				<P>3、采用此标准的页面，默认会在要元素上添加样式类：<span class="atn">class</span><span class="pun">=</span><span class="atv">"webview-rem"</span>；</P>
				<h3>引用方式</h3>
				<ul class="methods">
					<li class="explain">
						<dl class="expList">
							<dd style="height: 125px;">
								<p>
									引用方式一、
								</p>
								<pre class="prettyprint" data-lang="script" style="height: 95px;">
									&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="/static/js/libs/rem.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
								</pre>
							</dd>
							<dd style="height: 125px;">
							<p>
								引用方式二、
							</p>
							<pre class="prettyprint" data-lang="script" style="height: 95px;margin-left: -450px;">
								&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="/static/js/libs/require2.3.6.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
								&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;
										requirejs(["/static/js/libs/rem.js"]);
								&lt;/script&gt;
							</pre>
							</dd>
						</dl>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<h3>举例</h3>
				<ul class="methods">
					<li>
						<p>如果当前元素宽为750px时；</p>
						<p><span class="atn">width</span>:<span class="atv">7.5rem</span>;</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<p>如果当前元素宽为532px时；</p>
						<p><span class="atn">width</span>:<span class="atv">5.32rem</span>;</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</article>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/menu.js"></script>		
	</body>
</html>
